Call EXISTE_ADX("","","STOMAJ90",OKTRT) From ORDSYS
If OKTRT
  Call ECR_TRACE("************** MAJ STOMAJ90 ***************",-1) From GESECRAN
  Call MAJ From STOMAJ90 : # Moulinettes Stocks
Endif

Call EXISTE_ADX("","","GPAMAJ90",OKTRT) From ORDSYS
If OKTRT
  Call ECR_TRACE("************** MAJ GPAMAJ90 ***************",-1) From GESECRAN
  Call MAJ From GPAMAJ90 : # Moulinettes GPAO
Endif

Call EXISTE_ADX("","","CRMMAJ90",OKTRT) From ORDSYS
If OKTRT
  Call ECR_TRACE("************** MAJ CRMMAJ90 ***************",-1) From GESECRAN
  Call MAJ From CRMMAJ90 : # Moulinettes HDK (support client)
