Call EXISTE_ADX("","","FASMAJ90",OKTRT) From ORDSYS
If OKTRT
  Call ECR_TRACE("************** MAJ FASMAJ90 ***************",-1) From GESECRAN
  Call MAJ From FASMAJ90 : # Moulinettes Immobilisations
